This Brazilian comic belongs to The Cavern Clan set, a runoff of Mauricio de Sousas' Monica's Gang Brazilian comics.

His full name is Pithecanthropus Erectus da Silva and he's a hunter, he usually hunts dinosaurs or goes fishing in the river. He has a stalker named Tooga who always tries to marry him against his will.

He'll often make remarks which he shouldn't be able to know about given the Stone Age setting such as if they must walk long distances he'd say "Too bad they didn't invent the car yet, 'cause otherwise I would go faster."
